From 2ac2e12a2a3a4635c427964e47480ffa083928ae Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: CyberNeko-AI <cyberneko.ai@aosc.io>
Date: Sun, 8 Mar 2026 19:04:50 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 6/6] TG_OWT: Fix build with Pipewire 1.6

This fix is originally from the tg_owt repository:
Upstream Commit: d888bc3 (https://github.com/desktop-app/tg_owt/commit/d888bc3)

Since qt-6 also uses the WebRTC video_capture component and encounters
identical build failures against Pipewire 1.6, this fix is being introduced.
Note that the patch have been manually adjusted to match the QtWebEngine source.

Suggested-by: Björn Kettunen <bjorn.kettunen@thaodan.de>
Signed-off-by: CyberNeko-AI <cyberneko.ai@aosc.io>
---
 .../webrtc/modules/video_capture/linux/pipewire_session.cc       | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/qtwebengine/src/3rdparty/chromium/third_party/webrtc/modules/video_capture/linux/pipewire_session.cc b/qtwebengine/src/3rdparty/chromium/third_party/webrtc/modules/video_capture/linux/pipewire_session.cc
index cfe5350331..85aad349c0 100644
--- a/qtwebengine/src/3rdparty/chromium/third_party/webrtc/modules/video_capture/linux/pipewire_session.cc
+++ b/qtwebengine/src/3rdparty/chromium/third_party/webrtc/modules/video_capture/linux/pipewire_session.cc
@@ -15,6 +15,7 @@
 #include <spa/param/format.h>
 #include <spa/param/video/raw.h>
 #include <spa/pod/parser.h>
+#include <spa/pod/iter.h>
 
 #include <algorithm>
 
